---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy - CountTrackula">
  <section class="privacy">
    <h1>Privacy Policy for CountTrackula</h1>
    <p class="effective-date"><strong>Effective Date: 2025-01-01</strong></p>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to CountTrackula. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how CountTrackula handles your data when you use our progressive web app (PWA).</p>

    <h2>2. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula stores all of your tracking data locally on your device using your browser's built-in storage. We do not operate servers that collect, receive, or store your personal information.</p>
    <p>If you choose to enable Google Drive sync, your data is stored in your own Google Drive account under a folder created by CountTrackula. Fish Sauce Games does not have access to your Google Drive or the data stored within it.</p>

    <h2>3. Google Drive Integration</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula offers optional integration with Google Drive to synchronize your data across devices. When you enable this feature:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>You will be asked to authorize CountTrackula to access a specific folder in your Google Drive.</li>
      <li>Your tracking data is written directly to your Google Drive by your browser — it does not pass through our servers.</li>
      <li>You can revoke this access at any time through your <a href="https://myaccount.google.com/permissions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Account settings</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data We Do Not Collect</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula does not collect, transmit, or share:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name, email address, or any account information</li>
      <li>Your health, fitness, or nutrition data</li>
      <li>Your location</li>
      <li>Device identifiers or analytics</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data Export</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula allows you to export your data as JSON. This file stays on your device and is never transmitted to Fish Sauce Games.</p>

    <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>The only optional third-party integration is Google Drive, described above. CountTrackula does not use advertising networks, analytics services, or any other third-party data processors.</p>

    <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>CountTrackula is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from children.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>

    <h2>9. Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
    <p>Fish Sauce Games<br />Justin@FishSauceGames.com</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 860px;
  }

  .privacy h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .privacy h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .privacy p {
    color: #c0c8d8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .privacy ul {
    color: #c0c8d8;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .privacy ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .privacy a {
    color: #e05252;
  }

  .privacy a:hover {
    color: #ff7070;
  }

  .effective-date {
    color: #6b7a99 !important;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>
